<subSubSection id="11D265234547B645B595F9F8FE4D1A96" pageId="4" pageNumber="463" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="597736A84547B645B595F9F8FCDB1A42" blockId="4.[151,1437,1392,2031]" pageId="4" pageNumber="463">
<emphasis id="6BBCEABA4547B645B595F9F8FE801BFF" bold="true" box="[199,317,1645,1671]" pageId="4" pageNumber="463">Remarks:</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="3D594B594547B645B414F9F9FDBA1BFF" author="Majewski, E." box="[326,519,1644,1671]" pageId="4" pageNumber="463" pagination="1 - 39" refId="ref15526" refString="Majewski, E. (1885) Owady Zylkoskrzydle (Neuroptera Polonica). Systematyczny wykaz krajowych sieciarek i prasiatnic. Materyaly do fauny krajowej. Nakladem ksiegarni Teodora Paprockiego i S-ki, Warszawa, 1 - 2, 1 - 39." type="journal article" year="1885">Majewski (1885)</bibRefCitation>
reported this species as “pospol. w całym kraju” [
<emphasis id="6BBCEABA4547B645B115F9F8FF0B1BD2" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="463">common throughout the country</emphasis>
], meaning former territories of the Crown of the Kingdom of 
<collectingCountry id="21DF76384547B645B635F905FC051BD2" box="[871,952,1680,1706]" name="Poland" pageId="4" pageNumber="463">Poland</collectingCountry>
, which were separated in that time between the Russian and Austro-Hungarian Empires (including Halychyna within the current territory of 
<collectingCountry id="21DF76384547B645B1B1F921FAFE1BB7" box="[1251,1347,1716,1743]" name="Ukraine" pageId="4" pageNumber="463">Ukraine</collectingCountry>
). 
<bibRefCitation id="3D594B594547B645B004F920FF5F1B8B" author="Penny, N. D." pageId="4" pageNumber="463" pagination="141 - 217" refId="ref16477" refString="Penny, N. D. (1977) A systematic study of the family Boreidae (Mecoptera). The University of Kansas science bulletin, 51, 141 - 217." type="journal article" year="1977">Penny (1977)</bibRefCitation>
mentioned this species from the former territory of 
<collectingCountry id="21DF76384547B645B67CF94DFCC21B8A" box="[814,895,1752,1778]" name="Poland" pageId="4" pageNumber="463">Poland</collectingCountry>
, presumably based on previously published historical data. This idea is also confirmed by a published map on figure 81, where one of the distributional points is situated in the western part of 
<collectingCountry id="21DF76384547B645B4B8F8B5FDFA1A42" box="[490,583,1824,1850]" name="Ukraine" pageId="4" pageNumber="463">Ukraine</collectingCountry>
, close to the Carpathians.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="597736A84547B645B595F8D1FE181AFB" blockId="4.[151,1437,1392,2031]" pageId="4" pageNumber="463">
All data mentioned by 
<bibRefCitation id="3D594B594547B645B481F8D1FD0D1A27" author="Fudakowski, J." box="[467,688,1860,1887]" pageId="4" pageNumber="463" pagination="202 - 204" refId="ref14390" refString="Fudakowski, J. (1923) Znane i nowe stanowiska Borens hiemalis L. i B. westwoodi Hag. (Neuropteroidea - Mecoptera). (Neue und bekannte Standorte von Boreus hiemalis L. u. B. westwoodi Hag. in Polen). Polskie Pismo Entomologiczne, 2 (4), 202 - 204." type="journal article" year="1923">Fudakowski (1923)</bibRefCitation>
are based on J. Dziędzielewicz’s and E. Majewski’s reports (the same for 
<taxonomicName id="9EC84D2B4547B645B5ADF8FCFE291AFA" authorityName="Hagen" authorityYear="1866" box="[255,404,1896,1923]" class="Insecta" family="Boreidae" genus="Boreus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mecoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="463" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="westwoodi">
<emphasis id="6BBCEABA4547B645B5ADF8FCFEAD1AFA" box="[255,272,1897,1922]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="463">B</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="6BBCEABA4547B645B44CF8FDFE291AFA" box="[286,404,1896,1922]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="463">westwoodi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="597736A84547B645B595F819FE4D1A96" blockId="4.[151,1437,1392,2031]" pageId="4" pageNumber="463">
Mentioned by 
<bibRefCitation id="3D594B594547B645B439F819FDD11ADF" author="Dziedzielewicz, J." box="[363,620,1932,1959]" pageId="4" pageNumber="463" pagination="38 - 40" refId="ref14051" refString="Dziedzielewicz, J. (1918) Owady siatkoskrzydlowate ziem Polski (Insecta neuropteroidea Poloniae terrarum). Rozprawy i Wiadomo s ci z Muzeum im. Dzieduszyckich, Lwow, 4 (1 - 4), 38 - 40." type="journal article" year="1918">Dziędzielewicz (1918)</bibRefCitation>
, specimens of 
<taxonomicName id="9EC84D2B4547B645B641F818FC2E1ADE" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1767" box="[787,915,1932,1958]" class="Insecta" family="Boreidae" genus="Boreus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mecoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="463" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hyemalis">
<emphasis id="6BBCEABA4547B645B641F818FC2E1ADE" box="[787,915,1932,1958]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="463">P. hyemalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
